#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.180"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.180:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.180:0.2"
msgid "14. Oghavagga "
msgstr "14. Floods "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 180. Uddhambhāgiyasutta → uddhambhāgiyasaṃyojanasuttāni (bj)
msgctxt "sn45.180:0.3"
msgid "180. Uddhambhāgiyasutta "
msgstr "180. Higher Fetters "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.180:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, uddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are five higher fetters. "

msgctxt "sn45.180:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn45.180:1.3"
msgid "Rūparāgo, arūparāgo, māno, uddhaccaṃ, avijjā—"
msgstr "Desire for rebirth in the realm of luminous form, desire for rebirth in the formless realm, conceit, restlessness, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn45.180:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcuddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "These are the five higher fetters. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.180:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo. "
msgstr "The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these five higher fetters. "

msgctxt "sn45.180:1.6"
msgid "Katamo ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo? "
msgstr "What is the noble eightfold path? "

msgctxt "sn45.180:1.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.180:1.8"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabboti. "
msgstr "This is the noble eightfold path that should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these five higher fetters.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.62, sc2
msgctxt "sn45.180:2.1"
msgid "Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, uddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are five higher fetters. "

msgctxt "sn45.180:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn45.180:2.3"
msgid "Rūparāgo, arūparāgo, māno, uddhaccaṃ, avijjā—"
msgstr "Desire for rebirth in the realm of luminous form, desire for rebirth in the formless realm, conceit, restlessness, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn45.180:2.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcuddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "These are the five higher fetters. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.180:2.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo. "
msgstr "The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these five higher fetters. "

msgctxt "sn45.180:2.6"
msgid "Katamo ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo? "
msgstr "What is the noble eightfold path? "

msgctxt "sn45.180:2.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion …” "

msgctxt "sn45.180:2.8"
msgid "amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ … "
msgstr "“… which culminate, finish, and end in the deathless …” "

msgctxt "sn45.180:2.9"
msgid "nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ nibbānapabbhāraṃ. "
msgstr "“… which have extinguishment as their culmination, destination, and end. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.180:2.10"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti. "
msgstr "This is the noble eightfold path that should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these five higher fetters.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.180:2.11"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.180:2.12"
msgid "Oghavaggo aṭṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn45.180:3.1"
msgid "Ogho yogo upādānaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:3.2"
msgid "ganthaṃ anusayena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:3.3"
msgid "Kāmaguṇā nīvaraṇaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:3.4"
msgid "khandhā oruddhambhāgiyāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn45.180:4.1"
msgid "Avijjāvaggo paṭhamo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:4.2"
msgid "dutiyaṃ vihāraṃ vuccati; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:4.3"
msgid "Micchattaṃ tatiyo vaggo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:4.4"
msgid "catutthaṃ paṭipanneneva. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn45.180:5.1"
msgid "Titthiyaṃ pañcamo vaggo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:5.2"
msgid "chaṭṭho sūriyena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:5.3"
msgid "Bahukate sattamo vaggo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:5.4"
msgid "uppādo aṭṭhamena ca. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn45.180:6.1"
msgid "Divasavaggo navamo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:6.2"
msgid "Dasamo appamādena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:6.3"
msgid "Ekādasabalavaggo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:6.4"
msgid "Dvādasa esanā pāḷiyaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.180:6.5"
msgid "Oghavaggo bhavati terasāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn45.180:6.6"
msgid "Maggasaṃyuttaṃ paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on the Path is the first section."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
